description: With 15 years experience and a grand arsenal of festive carnival-themed food trailers, JND Amusements brings a ball of a time to Belchertown, indeed.Whether your event is in need of delicious cuisine (premium Hot Dogs, Corn Dogs, and Pizza), specialty beverages (Gourmet Coffee, Lemonade, and more), or crazy-tasty confections (including Cotton Candy, Caramel Apples, Popcorn, Nachos, and Hawaiian Ice), be worry-free because JND delivers all of the above, alongside a guarantee that everything will be handled with professional efficiency and quality, and there’s no doubt that everything about your party will go splendidly.
name: JND Amusements
